  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      lidocaine spray is used endocervical before office hysteroscopy to reduce the pain
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      5 sprays of Lidocaine is applied 3 minutes before office hysteroscopy
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
